---
title: Salisbury Steak-Style  Beyond Meat® Patties and Mash with Shallot Gravy and Apple Salad
description: We're breaking tradition and making this classic dish with Beyond Meat® instead of beef. A shallot gravy is poured over top and a creamy mash and refreshing side salad come alongside. The result is hearty, tasty and balanced — all in one meal!
